{"Id":489,"LanguageCodes":["zh","zho"],"Name":"zho-muhammadmakin","Author":"Muhammad Makin","Language":"Chinese(simplified)","Description":"Chinese(simplified)","Direction":"ltr","Source":"https://quranenc.com/check/chinese_makin/v1.0.0-csv.1 , https://quranenc.com/en/browse/chinese_makin , https://quranenc.com ,","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"当那件大事发生的时候，"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"没有任何人否认其发生。"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"那件大事将是能使人降级，能使人升级的；"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"当大地震荡，"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"山峦粉碎，"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":6,"Text":"化为散漫的尘埃，"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":7,"Text":"而你们分为三等的时候。"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":8,"Text":"幸福者，幸福者是何等的人？"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":9,"Text":"薄命者，薄命者是何等的人？"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":10,"Text":"最先行善者，是最先入乐园的人，"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":11,"Text":"这等人，确是蒙主眷顾的。"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":12,"Text":"他们在恩泽的乐园中。"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":13,"Text":"许多前人"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":14,"Text":"和少数后人，"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":15,"Text":"在珠宝镶成的床榻上，"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":16,"Text":"彼此相对地靠在上面。"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":17,"Text":"长生不老的僮仆，轮流着服待他们，"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":18,"Text":"捧着盏和壶，与满杯的醴泉；"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":19,"Text":"他们不因那醴泉而头痛，也不酩酊。"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":20,"Text":"他们有自己所选择的水果，"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":21,"Text":"和自己所爱好的鸟肉。"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":22,"Text":"还有白皙的、美目的妻子，"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":23,"Text":"好像藏在蚌壳里的珍珠一样。"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":24,"Text":"那是为了报酬他们的善行。"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":25,"Text":"他们在乐园里，听不到恶言和谎话，"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":26,"Text":"但听到说：祝你们平安！祝你们平安！"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":27,"Text":"幸福者，幸福者是何等的人？"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":28,"Text":"他们享受无刺的酸枣树，"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":29,"Text":"结实累累的（香蕉）树；"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":30,"Text":"漫漫的树荫；"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":31,"Text":"泛泛的流水；"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":32,"Text":"丰富的水果，"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":33,"Text":"四时不绝，可以随意摘食；"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":34,"Text":"与被升起的床榻。"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":35,"Text":"我使她们重新生长，"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":36,"Text":"我使她们常为处女，"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":37,"Text":"依恋丈夫，彼此同岁；"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":38,"Text":"这些都是幸福者所享受的。"}]}